title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-31-2014 FRI
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-31-2014 FRI....PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET 



 
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 01/31/14Friday, January 31, 2014


Glenn calls out MSNBC's recent behavior and says
             the NBC News brand is destroying itself... 

                  all while trying to imitate him.

 Glenn, Pat and Stu then have fun with listeners 
                for a Super Bowl edition of More-On Trivia. 

 In the third hour, Glenn expresses his intense frustration with
          the GOP and asks Americans to unite on the fact that they have been betrayed
              by their political parties.
